about us.description: Tau Epsilon Kappa is a co-ed professional technical fraternity committed to professional technical development as well as the advancement of social and academic excellence among the fraternity brothers. We strive to provide opportunities for our members to explore their technical interests and further their relationships in both a social and professional environment. Tau Epsilon Kappa fosters members who are passionate to cultivate their skills to help better the community, as well as encourage a diverse, inclusive, and equal community.
